text: Walterswil is the name of three places in Switzerland: * Walterswil, Solothurn, a municipality in the district of Olten * Walterswil, Berne, a municipality in the district of Trachselwald (today administrative district of Oberaargau) * Walterswil, Zug (Walterswil-Sihlbrugg), part of Baar
title: Walterswil
